OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA few clear
OL,6,Fspells during Monday evening and
OL,7,Fovernight but often cloudy, this
OL,8,Flowering to produce mist and spots of
OL,9,Fdrizzle over the hills. Otherwise,
OL,10,Fremaining dry but breezy. A mid night.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FMostly dry but a rather grey
OL,13,Fday overall with cloud only slowly
OL,14,Flifting and breaking. Some warm and
OL,15,Fbrighter spells are possible, mainly
OL,16,Fin the south. Winds easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
