OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FTurning brighter over the next few
OL,7,Fdays with spells of strong sunshine.
OL,8,FTemperatures climbing and starting to
OL,9,Ffeel hot in the south. Staying dry
OL,10,Fwith light winds.
